# Docusaurus guides

- Follow `GUIDE-STANDARD.md` for content structure and pedagogy.
- Keep lessons linear and self-contained — no "you should already know X."
- Do not break doc IDs or sidebar paths without updating cross-links.
- Use `make dev` (npm start) to preview doc changes.
